WEBVTT

00:06.000 --> 00:12.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

00:12.730 --> 00:15.131
What the hell?

00:21.205 --> 00:24.274
Hey. Hey. Hey!

00:28.412 --> 00:29.813
No, no! No! No!

00:29.815 --> 00:30.780
Get him out!

00:30.782 --> 00:32.314
Get out of the truck!

00:34.653 --> 00:37.153
Let me go. Let me go.

00:39.757 --> 00:41.257
Take the truck.

00:41.259 --> 00:42.926
Take the wallet,
take the phone, okay?

00:42.928 --> 00:44.427
Just... I won't say a word.

00:44.429 --> 00:46.229
Damn right you won't say a word.

00:48.799 --> 00:51.000
'Cause I know
who you are

00:51.002 --> 00:53.303
and where you live.

00:53.305 --> 00:55.605
Okay, I swear. Take the truck.

00:55.607 --> 00:57.807
I won't say a damn thing
to nobody.

00:57.809 --> 01:00.276
I believe you.

01:11.088 --> 01:13.056
30 years old?

01:13.058 --> 01:14.891
That's what it says
on the label.

01:14.893 --> 01:17.126
30-year-old Rebel Tears.

01:17.128 --> 01:18.528
That stuff's impossible to get.

01:18.530 --> 01:20.163
I know a guy.

01:20.165 --> 01:21.764
How'd you afford it?
Me and 11 guys

01:21.766 --> 01:23.166
went in on a case.

01:23.168 --> 01:25.101
My guy got us a discount.

01:25.103 --> 01:26.169
Still.
- Hey,

01:26.171 --> 01:28.471
when opportunity knocks,
you answer.

01:28.473 --> 01:30.673
Enter.

01:33.210 --> 01:35.111
I can't just stand
by and not notice

01:35.113 --> 01:36.846
if you guys are
drinking in here.

01:36.848 --> 01:39.749
Nah, we're not drinking;
we're just admiring.

01:39.751 --> 01:42.986
30-year-old Rebel Tears.
Whatever that is.

01:42.988 --> 01:44.921
Liquid gold.
- I'm not crackin' it.

01:44.923 --> 01:45.989
Nope.

01:46.824 --> 01:48.825
So, I just got a phone call

01:48.827 --> 01:50.426
from my old sergeant.

01:50.428 --> 01:52.095
He made captain a few weeks ago,

01:52.097 --> 01:55.064
and they gave him
Group 1 at IAB.

01:55.066 --> 01:55.965
Captain Bullman.

01:55.967 --> 01:58.635
He asked me
to come work with him.

02:00.771 --> 02:03.539
In his group,
answering directly to him.

02:04.375 --> 02:06.409
Wow, that's great, Abby.

02:06.411 --> 02:07.677
Congratulations!

02:07.679 --> 02:09.679
It's staying sealed.
We all get it.

02:09.681 --> 02:11.714
You gonna take it?

02:11.716 --> 02:13.316
I don't know.

02:13.318 --> 02:15.285
I wanted to talk
to you guys first.

02:15.287 --> 02:19.022
Boss is gonna be, I don't know,
I can't even imagine.

02:19.024 --> 02:20.623
Well, that's a big part
of my hesitation.

02:20.625 --> 02:22.125
What do you think
I should do?

02:22.127 --> 02:24.294
Go back in time
and not tell us about it?

02:24.296 --> 02:27.096
I promise I will not tell him
that we spoke about this.

02:27.098 --> 02:28.298
Actually, you won't have to.

02:28.300 --> 02:30.099
He'll just know.
Not if you don't tell him.

02:30.101 --> 02:32.902
He'll just know in that way
that he just knows stuff.

02:36.640 --> 02:39.142
I have been with him
going on nine years.

02:39.144 --> 02:41.711
Great years, but I've gone
from being detective

02:41.713 --> 02:43.846
to Miss Moneypenny.
- Abby,

02:43.848 --> 02:45.515
he really values your smarts.

02:45.517 --> 02:46.950
Anybody could see that.

02:46.952 --> 02:50.153
I know. I just feel like a
small fish in a big pond.

02:50.155 --> 02:51.387
This is hard.

02:51.389 --> 02:53.122
I hear you.
It's one of those things

02:53.124 --> 02:54.757
that's "nothing personal"

02:54.759 --> 02:57.660
that gets taken
as "very personal."

02:57.662 --> 03:01.631
By a man I owe and admire
more than I can say.

03:06.870 --> 03:09.706
♪

03:24.055 --> 03:25.755
Are you okay?

03:25.757 --> 03:26.756
Help me.

03:26.758 --> 03:27.991
Are you all right?

03:27.993 --> 03:28.992
Help me, please!

03:28.994 --> 03:29.959
Are you all right?

03:29.961 --> 03:30.994
Come here.
He's trying to kill me!

03:30.996 --> 03:32.128
Okay, it's okay.

03:32.130 --> 03:34.163
- Where do you think you're going?!
- Let her go!

03:35.399 --> 03:38.301
Let her go!

03:39.571 --> 03:41.738
I got you.

03:44.109 --> 03:46.075
Oh, my God.
Oh, my God.

03:46.077 --> 03:47.477
It's okay. It's okay.

03:47.479 --> 03:48.778
I've got you, I've got you.

03:48.780 --> 03:50.613
You're gonna be okay, all right?

03:50.615 --> 03:52.315
Okay.

03:52.317 --> 03:54.417
Hey! Police! Police!

03:54.419 --> 03:56.486
Hey! What's going on?
- Hey!

03:56.488 --> 03:58.321
Hurry! Please hurry!

03:58.323 --> 04:00.323
You have to help the others!

04:00.325 --> 04:01.591
Others?

04:01.593 --> 04:03.459
There's a guy in there
trying to kill her!

04:03.461 --> 04:04.794
Stay put.

04:04.796 --> 04:05.796
Go.

04:06.563 --> 04:08.364
Police!

04:08.366 --> 04:10.500
Police.

04:30.120 --> 04:32.055
Door.

04:36.527 --> 04:37.894
You set?
- Go. Yes.

04:37.896 --> 04:40.163
Police! Don't move!

04:40.165 --> 04:41.597
Police! Don't move!

04:41.599 --> 04:43.900
You got it?
- Go, go.

04:46.638 --> 04:49.072
You're gonna be okay.

04:50.575 --> 04:52.308
Anybody else in here
with you guys?

04:52.310 --> 04:53.976
Just stay put. We're
gonna help you out.

04:53.978 --> 04:55.478
Eddie, I got two more.

04:55.480 --> 04:56.779
Call it in.

04:56.781 --> 04:59.148
Central, 12-David.
10-85 forthwith.

04:59.150 --> 05:01.184
I got multiple hostages
at this location.

05:01.186 --> 05:03.086
And we got
one under.

05:05.856 --> 05:09.856
<b><font color="#00FF00">♪ Blue Bloods 8x10 ♪</font></b>
<font color="#00FFFF">Heavy Is the Head</font>
